metadata.name: Voyage
metadata.description:
‘VOYAGE’ Live open edition for free mint to anyone who wishes to claim it, it’s an accessible gift for all to experience and enjoy the beauty of Art, Film photography and Web3. Share with everyone.

First of the roll portrayed on 35mm film. Colombian photographer Edwin Garcia’s series ‘Voyage’ tells a story of a psychedelic woman under the influence of her own ecstasy. The pictures represent the battle between true self & alter ego, drawing the most sensual, daring & honest sides of Sofía Martinich.
